    %% External to Ingress flows
    Client -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>None/Bearer Token"| IstioGW
    Client -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>None"| OSRoute

    %% Serverless path
    IstioGW -->|"HTTP/80<br/>mTLS (Istio STRICT)<br/>Service Identity"| KnativeGW
    KnativeGW -->|"HTTP/80<br/>mTLS (Istio)<br/>Service Identity"| PredictorSL

    %% Raw deployment path
    OSRoute -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (serving cert)<br/>OpenShift OAuth"| OAuthProxy
    OAuthProxy -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>None (localhost)<br/>Trusted proxy"| PredictorRaw

    %% Control plane flows
    ControllerMgr -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token"| K8sAPI

    %% Storage init flows
    StorageInit -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM"| S3
    StorageInit -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>GCP SA"| GCS
    StorageInit -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Azure creds"| Azure
    StorageInit -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Registry creds"| OCI

